title: Ce$_{5}$Ga$_{7}$Rh$_{12}$ Structure
comments:
This is the ternary version of \href{current_web_home_dir/A5B19_hR24_166_a2c_b3c2h-001}{the Ce$_{5}$Co$_{19}$ structure}. We have arbitrarily chosen Ce$_{5}$Ga$_{7}$Rh$_{12}$ as the prototype. 
 \href{current_web_home_dir/A4B5C9_hR18_166_2c_a2c_dh-001}{Ce$_{4}$Ga$_{5}$Rh$_{9}$} and \href{current_web_home_dir/A7B11C18_hR36_166_a3c_b5c_3h-001}{Ce$_{7}$Ga$_{11}$Rh$_{18}$} are slightly gallium-enriched forms of this structure.
